title: [Burghal Enclave, Great Dome]
description: The high ceiling overhead is a dome, carved out of the overhanging rock itself.  Protrusions of glimaerstone in the tufa are organic and patternless, streaking the white stone with bands of green, gold, and lilac.  Several stout chairs surround a large vat centered directly beneath the dome.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
